Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,「高嶺之花被學生全員侵犯」被輪姦的新任女教師 \N星宮一花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,大家好 初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.77,0:00:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫星宮一花
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.20,0:00:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,今天开始要和大家一起学习
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,专任科目是国语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.38,0:00:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.69,0:00:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,给我安静
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.82,0:00:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,星宮老师将担任这班的副指导老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.48,0:00:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:00:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,上任第一天过来拜访
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不用太拘束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲还好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,很久见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.82,0:01:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.19,0:01:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,亲戚？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.99,0:01:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那是靠关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.03,0:01:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.99,0:01:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,采用考试最高分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在校园中若有担心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.83,0:01:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管说 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.87,0:01:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就很放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.00,0:01:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,听说校长今年就要退休
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.84,0:01:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,正为了下次校长选战准备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,间谍？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,说的不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.25,0:01:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,校园内的老师有派系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,最大的派系都是第一线公职人员
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.86,0:01:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但是却没什么好风评
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.49,0:01:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,视情况 下任校长\N我想由从外面招聘会较好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,橄榄球社要废社？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.17,0:01:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,理事会议上己提出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.17,0:01:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.81,0:02:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.84,0:02:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,若是理事长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,为了要帮助自己的血亲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.58,0:02:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很容易改变方针吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.48,0:02:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是再小的事情\N希望你能报告给我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.47,0:02:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那今天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,来教很容易错的nu的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,在现代的日语 若说到nu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,就是指不是什么什么\N否定的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,而这种用法\N我们叫做yaranu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,文言文上也当然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:02:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是用来指否定之意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,还有另外一种意思代表结束的nu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那就请看这
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,圈圈一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,花开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,圈圈二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有棵未开花之树
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有谁知道正确的解释
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎没人知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,答案是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,圈圈一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,花已开了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 圈圈二的答案是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.00,0:04:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,有棵没有开花的树
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,圈圈一的nu因为在句末
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是终止形
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,所以是完成状态的nu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.86,0:05:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,圈圈二的nu呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,因为在树这名词前面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,所以是否定的nu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,大家明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那接着要来做上周所说的汉宇测验
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,有好好念书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,传下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.87,0:05:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,请传下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那会计算时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.99,0:06:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,请开始作答
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,好 停笔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那就按顺序传回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.50,0:09:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,从后面传回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,若好好预习就没问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.17,0:09:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那今天就到这
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,班长 下课
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,立正 敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:10:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,用力点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那进展呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,学生偷拍先按兵不动 视情况而定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,若这件事浮上台面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,校园将会没有信用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,未成年犯罪将是我们的污点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,事情发展顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,若有个万一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.33,0:16:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,事情没照我们所想发展
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己和立场主任
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是和下任校长的立场老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.10,0:16:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,会追随到最后的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.48,0:16:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,星宮老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.98,0:16:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有话想说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.99,0:16:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,学生做这种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,现在在这里删掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,学生家里还有备份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我先跟理事长报告
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样做比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这很严重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,理事长肯定会放过的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.18,0:17:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,理事长是学校经营者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.02,0:17:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,若这件事浮上台面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定会影响明年的入学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.20,0:17:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就可以解决的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,只跟主任报告
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,主任老师吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我看还是跟理事长报告
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,一听到主任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,为何就这样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,梨本
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不要拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么办呢？梨本
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,星宮老师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎想严惩你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,偷拍是犯罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,最好的状况也是退学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,弄个不好也许会被逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么办呢？梨本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去 橄榄球部也会退社哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是追随内田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,真是可靠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,现在要做的事 全都记录拍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.11,0:19:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,味道真香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,味道真香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,梨本看一下啊 这嘴唇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,梨本有好好在拍吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,正在拍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真的有很漂亮的嘴唇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,来确认一下感触
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.98,0:22:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快看这啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很漂亮耶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.99,0:22:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,梨本想再看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.50,0:22:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,还想再看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,再多拍点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.17,0:23:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没反应吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.78,0:23:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,脸有在动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.48,0:23:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好拍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.50,0:24:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,睡着了 乳头却有反应呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.78,0:24:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,非常敏感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.98,0:24:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.48,0:25:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这边会怎样反应呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.99,0:25:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,乳头 真期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.48,0:26:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒的腿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.49,0:26:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那边湿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.20,0:26:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,已经湿了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.79,0:27:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真下流的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.50,0:27:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不要弄醒 好好看着
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.50,0:28:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真害羞的姿势啊 ，没…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.00,0:28:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,碰触到了 有动了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.50,0:28:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,从刚就一直在微动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.18,0:29:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好像要出来了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.49,0:29:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,插得很深呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.48,0:29:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,再插更进去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.47,0:30:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,身体还没反应呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.21,0:30:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,从刚才嘴巴就一直在动着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.35,0:30:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我看着有没有醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.28,0:30:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,会好好看着的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.79,0:30:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,内田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.00,0:32:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,进去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.00,0:33:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,手指
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.87,0:33:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,把小穴打开了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.48,0:33:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,立刻就插进去了耶 梨本
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.28,0:33:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,要看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.78,0:33:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了 刚好插进去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.49,0:33:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.00,0:33:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,睡着了也这样有感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.20,0:33:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.47,0:34:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,碰触到了才会动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.18,0:34:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,从刚才就颤抖地动着耶
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.49,0:34:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,梦见很舒服的梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.49,0:35:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,梨本帮我架住
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.56,0:36:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,星宮老师越来越湿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.93,0:36:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,从刚才脚就颤抖地动着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.50,0:36:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,睡着了也这样有感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.49,0:36:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,也帮我把她屁股露出来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.50,0:36:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不要弄醒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.48,0:37:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,快看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.48,0:37:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,超漂亮的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.47,0:38:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.48,0:38:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,丁字内裤刚刚好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.49,0:38:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,兴奋起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.50,0:39:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,穿这内裤超有光泽的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.49,0:39:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,有反应了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.49,0:39:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这样舔了也完全不醒耶
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.52,0:40:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,老师的身材超漂亮的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.49,0:40:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,能拍到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.50,0:40:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.49,0:40:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要舔吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.13,0:40:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是 想要舔
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.50,0:40:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,随你喜欢舔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.47,0:40:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,随我喜欢做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.98,0:41:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,味道很香吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.19,0:41:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,味道超香的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.19,0:41:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这嘴唇吃没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.49,0:41:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.77,0:41:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.48,0:41:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,已经兴奋了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.48,0:41:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这样怎可能还不兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.19,0:41:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,想舔小穴吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.49,0:41:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.20,0:41:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.50,0:42:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,很完美地嵌进去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.48,0:42:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,梨本
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.39,0:42:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,老师有反应了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.50,0:42:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,被你这样吃很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.20,0:42:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那唾液弄太多
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.00,0:42:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,很想要你的肉棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.48,0:42:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,梨本
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.02,0:42:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,把肉棒塞进嘴巴里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.49,0:42:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.50,0:43:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,想要她继续睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.48,0:43:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在做什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.48,0:43:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你把她弄醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.05,0:43:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,压住她
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.99,0:43:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.99,0:44:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,星宮老师 叫也不会有人
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.20,0:44:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.26,0:44:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,都说叫也没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.50,0:44:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,今天教员都下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.47,0:44:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没社团活动 学生也不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.47,0:44:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,叫也没用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.98,0:44:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.18,0:44:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么办呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.49,0:44:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.49,0:44:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.19,0:44:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,外面的 气质教师
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.10,0:44:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,偷拍被发现 这家伙要退学
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.97,0:44:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,学生的人生就白费了\N这样可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.84,0:44:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我会跟理事长说不要退学
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.98,0:44:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,靠关系的人真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.75,0:44:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.48,0:45:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,内田老师 要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.99,0:45:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,压住她
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.99,0:45:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,连梨本你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.09,0:45:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.86,0:45:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真危险呢 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.50,0:45:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.00,0:45:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.00,0:45:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.47,0:45:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,梨本
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.17,0:45:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.44,0:45:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好好压住哦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.18,0:45:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.48,0:45:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.58,0:45:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,都说过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.22,0:45:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.49,0:45:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,给我压住她
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.20,0:45:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.50,0:45:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.24,0:45:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.91,0:45:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.28,0:46:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.98,0:46:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.18,0:46:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.19,0:46:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.50,0:46:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.50,0:46:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再挣扎了 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.31,0:46:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,连梨本也
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.31,0:46:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.98,0:46:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.49,0:46:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.49,0:46:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.47,0:47:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.48,0:47:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.49,0:47:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.50,0:47:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,老师快看这边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.50,0:47:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.50,0:47:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很认真地拍着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.57,0:47:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不要拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.61,0:47:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.41,0:47:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.48,0:47:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.99,0:47:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.50,0:48:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来救我 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.50,0:48:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就说不会有人来了啊 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.47,0:48:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,快住…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.50,0:48:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.48,0:48:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.61,0:48:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.48,0:48:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.49,0:49:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.06,0:49:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.73,0:49:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.80,0:49:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,才没这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.49,0:49:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,已经够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.47,0:49:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,已经满足了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.48,0:50:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,还没满足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.49,0:50:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.50,0:50:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 求求你 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.17,0:50:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.49,0:50:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.06,0:50:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,都说放过我了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.99,0:51:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.49,0:51:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.47,0:51:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.27,0:51:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.91,0:51:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.25,0:51:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.58,0:51:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.99,0:51:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,请快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.49,0:51:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.00,0:51:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,朝这边
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.07,0:51:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那边也好好拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.47,0:52:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.48,0:52:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.48,0:52:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.78,0:52:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,快住
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.49,0:52:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.18,0:52:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,梨本你也想插进去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.46,0:52:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.16,0:52:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,朝向这个
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.99,0:52:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你来做
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.39,0:52:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.20,0:53:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.50,0:53:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.47,0:53:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.48,0:53:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.31,0:53:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翘高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.49,0:53:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.15,0:53:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.99,0:53:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去了哦 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.26,0:53:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.50,0:53:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.40,0:53:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.48,0:53:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.48,0:53:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,星宮老师的小穴舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.89,0:53:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,超棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.56,0:54:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有好好拍进去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.46,0:54:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不要说那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.99,0:54:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,朝这边啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.80,0:54:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.77,0:54:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,老师和精子很配呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.48,0:54:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.18,0:54:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.49,0:54:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,能说非常舒服吗？老师
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.00,0:54:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不想说那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.50,0:54:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,看得出很舒服 肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.94,0:54:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.48,0:54:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.48,0:55:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,梨本也射给老师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.79,0:55:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,还想要精子吧 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.49,0:55:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,老师说一下想要精子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.43,0:55:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,想要精子
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.03,0:55:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,有说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.98,0:55:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.48,0:55:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.00,0:55:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.48,0:56:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.50,0:56:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.48,0:56:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.98,0:56:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.55,0:56:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.45,0:56:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.36,0:56:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要接受学生啊 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.19,0:56:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.50,0:56:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.09,0:57:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.19,0:57:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事若想跟理事长报告\N那就请便
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.20,0:57:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,把我们都牵扯出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.84,0:57:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,反正影片会一直都在
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.97,0:57:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.50,0:58:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那接着要发昨天的测验
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.31,0:58:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,叫到名字到前面来拿
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.11,0:58:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,龟田
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.18,0:58:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,池田浩
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.99,0:58:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,梨本
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.99,0:58:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,老师今天罗穿裤子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.20,0:58:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,加藤
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.97,0:58:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,村田
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.49,0:58:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,若想跟理事长报告 那就请便
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.99,0:59:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,把我们都牵扯出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.99,0:59:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,反正影片会一直都在
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.49,0:59:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.97,0:59:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.51,0:59:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,理事长 有事想找您商量
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.18,0:59:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.65,0:59:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我商量也没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.98,1:00:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,理事长也已经回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.49,1:00:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么是要商量的呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.19,1:00:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.59,1:00:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么事
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.89,1:00:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.00,1:00:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,已经听内田老师说了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.20,1:00:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不断做些奇怪的小动作
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.67,1:00:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,被学生偷拍影片
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.81,1:00:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是一伙的吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.74,1:00:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,都不听人说话的耶
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.85,1:00:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我看了你的影片
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.48,1:00:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,很可怜 想要保护你
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.99,1:00:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,所以留在这里哦
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.49,1:00:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,若跟理事长报告
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.99,1:00:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,让他看了影片
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.89,1:00:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,学校会变不安定
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.50,1:00:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是 若影片流到网上
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.00,1:00:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,会成为一生的伤痛哦
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.97,1:00:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不能做奇怪的小动作
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.44,1:01:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,谁都没好处
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.48,1:01:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,为了遮掩
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.32,1:01:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不是裙子而牛字裤啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.69,1:01:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我来保护你哦
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.19,1:01:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,请快住手 主任
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.53,1:01:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝对会保密的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.50,1:01:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.00,1:01:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,腰真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.48,1:01:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.81,1:01:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只看影片没办法满足的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.62,1:01:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不这样抚弄的话
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.19,1:01:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的你啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.02,1:01:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是扑向蛇的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.66,1:01:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.19,1:01:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是羚羊呢 这双腿
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.13,1:01:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,请快住手
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.00,1:01:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.48,1:02:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮的腿啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.49,1:02:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好好地让我看
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.50,1:02:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,很瘦又很长
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.47,1:02:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但这边却很有肉呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.48,1:02:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.98,1:02:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真极品
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.50,1:03:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,腰骨在这位置啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.20,1:03:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,果然脚很长呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.31,1:03:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒耶
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.49,1:03:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这边也转过来
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.98,1:03:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,滑溜溜地呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.48,1:03:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这真受不了耶
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.49,1:04:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这里蛮多肉的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.96,1:04:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,腰跟脚连接这边
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.77,1:04:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真是艺术品呢
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.98,1:04:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这个这个
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.49,1:04:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就说不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.00,1:04:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,让我好好地看
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.40,1:04:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.03,1:04:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,手靠在这边
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.09,1:05:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.99,1:05:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.80,1:05:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮又瘦
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.47,1:05:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.17,1:05:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这边很有肉
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.65,1:05:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来很好吃的腿呢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.99,1:05:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很完美了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.42,1:05:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,完美哦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.48,1:06:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好灼热
Dialogue: 0,1:06:08.18,1:06:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,身体中心果然很灼热呢
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.99,1:06:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,像是太阳高高挂
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.50,1:06:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.00,1:06:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.97,1:07:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,内裤透出来 看得见呢
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.48,1:07:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.98,1:07:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这里啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.25,1:07:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,内裤线条露出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.98,1:07:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,薄薄地透出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.35,1:07:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,穿着深色的内裤
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.62,1:07:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.66,1:07:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不是白色的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.20,1:07:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,内裤透出来 看得见
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.47,1:07:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是蓝色的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.48,1:07:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,内裤线条透出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.61,1:07:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.19,1:07:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这样会兴奋呢
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.78,1:08:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,想看内裤啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.48,1:08:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在说什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.49,1:08:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是绿色的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.30,1:08:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为是蓝色的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.49,1:09:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这真受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.48,1:09:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不能做这种事
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.98,1:09:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就只是看一下摸一下而已
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.35,1:09:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,更没打算做
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.20,1:09:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,叫出这种的声音
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.47,1:10:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.41,1:10:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.97,1:10:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,陷进去好深哦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.49,1:11:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你的美丽双腿
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.19,1:11:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真美丽的屁股
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.49,1:11:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,内裤居然这样
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.36,1:11:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,陷进去啊
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.50,1:11:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.04,1:11:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,星宮老师
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.47,1:11:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,主任老师 这样很为难
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.48,1:11:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,朝向这边
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.99,1:11:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这里非常有魅力呢
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.00,1:12:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.48,1:12:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.52,1:12:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,星宮老师
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.99,1:12:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这边很有感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.48,1:12:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,主任老师
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.38,1:12:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,打算要做什么
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.99,1:12:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就只是看一下
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.79,1:12:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.26,1:12:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,就只是看而已
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.30,1:13:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,胸部曲线真可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.50,1:13:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,老实点
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.50,1:13:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好好听我的话
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.17,1:13:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,影片若流到网上
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.74,1:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,会很困扰吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.98,1:13:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,会很困扰
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.79,1:14:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,会永远消除不去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.47,1:14:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,溢出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.48,1:14:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,溢出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:14:30.99,1:14:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这…的线
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.49,1:14:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,胸罩这样溢了出来
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.47,1:14:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.18,1:14:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,为何？
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.98,1:15:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是喔 因为敏感吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.15,1:15:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,太有感觉了？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.99,1:15:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真害羞？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.49,1:15:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:15:13.80,1:15:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,接着不想再被摸了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.00,1:15:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,想要停手
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.97,1:15:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是无法停手啊
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.51,1:15:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这样漂亮的身体就在眼前呢
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.20,1:15:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,露出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.50,1:15:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.50,1:16:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.33,1:16:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,果然很有感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.87,1:16:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.97,1:16:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,星宮老师
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.77,1:16:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.48,1:16:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.19,1:16:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,听不见
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.69,1:16:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.66,1:16:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.52,1:16:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要再多抚弄些吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.39,1:16:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.00,1:16:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么求我？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.17,1:16:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不能做这种事
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.97,1:17:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,漂亮的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.34,1:17:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样都很想抚摸
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.41,1:17:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,太漂亮了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.50,1:17:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,能舔吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.48,1:18:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就说不行
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.98,1:18:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.50,1:19:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.60,1:19:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不能再继续
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.47,1:20:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好灼热
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.47,1:20:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴越来越灼热了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.18,1:20:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.49,1:20:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,腰在动了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.10,1:20:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不错哦
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.50,1:20:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,刚好碰触到舒服的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.47,1:21:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,腰正在动呢
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.98,1:21:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.49,1:21:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴巴说不要
Dialogue: 0,1:21:14.99,1:21:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,身体很舒服的动着呢
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.00,1:21:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就说不是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.99,1:21:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,放轻松
Dialogue: 0,1:21:49.09,1:21:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,把脚给我伸长
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.50,1:21:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,脚伸长用力磨蹭很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.70,1:22:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,会用力磨蹭啊
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.98,1:22:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,1:22:20.49,1:22:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不错哦
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.72,1:22:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮的女人
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.49,1:23:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.00,1:23:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不行
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.63,1:23:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,变舒服了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.97,1:23:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,变舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.48,1:23:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.99,1:23:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.79,1:23:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你 主任老师
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.99,1:23:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,变舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.00,1:23:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.50,1:23:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.49,1:24:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有小穴的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.50,1:24:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,看见了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.50,1:24:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要看那种地方
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.97,1:24:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,脸虽也很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.98,1:24:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴跟屁洞也很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.98,1:25:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,果然漂亮的人\N全身不管哪都漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.49,1:25:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.50,1:25:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在做什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.83,1:25:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,主任先生
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.30,1:25:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在舔屁洞啊
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.91,1:25:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,明明就知道
Dialogue: 0,1:25:58.91,1:26:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很难舔 再抬上来点
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.48,1:26:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就好
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.42,1:26:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要舔了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.49,1:26:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,尽情舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.50,1:26:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.50,1:26:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,屁洞很有感觉吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.50,1:27:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,才没有感觉到
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.50,1:27:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,主任老师
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.30,1:27:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这样舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.99,1:28:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.48,1:28:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,白色真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.48,1:28:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,腰围这样 却有这样的双腿
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.42,1:28:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,又细又长的双腿 忍耐
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.00,1:28:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这个\N做什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.47,1:28:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.48,1:28:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,快舔
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.48,1:28:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.49,1:29:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法做
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.99,1:29:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,影片若流到网上会很困扰吧
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.50,1:29:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,为了不变成那样\N我会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.44,1:29:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微亲一下
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.67,1:29:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,就只亲一下
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.50,1:29:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴唇真柔软
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.47,1:29:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好有弹性
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.99,1:30:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不错哦 星宮老师
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.30,1:30:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样继续下去
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.20,1:30:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.20,1:30:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,若好好听话
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.50,1:31:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.20,1:31:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,腿很漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.78,1:31:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那样的小蛮腰
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.48,1:31:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,全都很赞呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.19,1:31:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.33,1:31:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了耶 这样的
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.47,1:32:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉到了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.98,1:32:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,身体很敏感呢
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.48,1:32:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,再舔一次
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.49,1:32:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,过来这边
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.49,1:32:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,刚不是做过了？
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.19,1:33:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,再一次
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.49,1:33:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样吃着 不要说话哦
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.69,1:33:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.36,1:33:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这边啊
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.49,1:34:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.98,1:34:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,星宮老师
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.98,1:35:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,来帮你插下面的嘴巴吧
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.47,1:35:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,已经受不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:27.98,1:35:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,过来这边
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.49,1:35:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.49,1:35:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真的请快住手
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.50,1:35:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真敢说呢
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.30,1:35:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,超湿的耶
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.50,1:35:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,唾液流出很多了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:35:59.47,1:36:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.48,1:36:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.91,1:36:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.05,1:36:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.89,1:36:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.49,1:36:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.97,1:36:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.99,1:36:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:36:51.99,1:36:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.19,1:36:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.00,1:36:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.50,1:37:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我会全部保密的
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.48,1:37:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然知道你会
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.84,1:37:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但进去了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.99,1:37:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手 求求你
Dialogue: 0,1:37:25.49,1:37:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.10,1:37:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.99,1:37:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.50,1:38:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就说不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.00,1:38:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 我
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.98,1:38:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.48,1:38:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.98,1:38:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.50,1:39:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,又进去了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.50,1:39:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,请放过我
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.97,1:39:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,腰停不下来
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.27,1:39:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不行
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.67,1:39:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,现在腰…停不下来
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.48,1:39:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.50,1:39:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.97,1:39:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要插进这样深
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.49,1:40:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.49,1:40:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.99,1:40:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.00,1:40:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,主任老师
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.27,1:40:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.00,1:40:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:40:56.47,1:40:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉越来越奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.91,1:41:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉变奇怪了？
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.48,1:41:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.48,1:41:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.47,1:41:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.98,1:41:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,腰停不下来
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.49,1:41:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.50,1:41:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手 求求你
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.00,1:42:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,躺下来
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.00,1:42:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.97,1:42:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.98,1:42:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我要尽情抽插
Dialogue: 0,1:42:44.48,1:42:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,已经够了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.50,1:43:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.48,1:44:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,插进好深哦
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.92,1:44:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.99,1:44:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,主任老师的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.79,1:44:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,非常大
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.19,1:44:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,也没不好呢
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.19,1:45:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,插进去好里面
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.00,1:45:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.00,1:45:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.50,1:45:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.47,1:46:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,主任老师
Dialogue: 0,1:46:01.08,1:46:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.98,1:46:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好激烈
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.49,1:46:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,1:46:18.49,1:46:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.66,1:46:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.86,1:46:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.80,1:46:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.03,1:46:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:46:25.10,1:46:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.20,1:46:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.70,1:46:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.00,1:46:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.98,1:46:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬 硬梆梆的
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.72,1:46:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,射了射了
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.92,1:46:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.48,1:47:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,射好多
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.49,1:47:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.99,1:47:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在做什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.69,1:47:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.53,1:48:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,拍照啊
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.73,1:48:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.80,1:48:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种地方做爱
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.53,1:48:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是亲戚的理事长\N也无法说吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:11.47,1:48:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 请快住手
Dialogue: 0,1:48:21.98,1:48:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.99,1:48:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.18,1:51:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,光源氏去世后
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.62,1:51:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,故事以薰为中心展开
Dialogue: 0,1:51:21.50,1:51:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,舞台横跨都城和宇治
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.00,1:51:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,老师？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.97,1:51:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.97,1:51:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,没事哦
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.98,1:51:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,光源氏的义母阿八的房间
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.08,1:51:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,在北边
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.99,1:51:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,酒干枯之后
Dialogue: 0,1:51:49.29,1:51:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,伴随着两人的秘密
Dialogue: 0,1:51:52.53,1:51:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,到宇治去隐居
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.00,1:52:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.50,1:52:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,薰几乎每天拜访
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.48,1:52:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,老师？
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.98,1:52:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没事哦
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.98,1:52:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,各位请先自习
Dialogue: 0,1:52:19.99,1:52:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,老师先回一下教职员室
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.12,1:52:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,去拿一下资料
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.48,1:52:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,放任上课不管 这样不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:52:47.48,1:52:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:52:49.98,1:52:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,成为老师是从小的梦想
Dialogue: 0,1:52:56.99,1:52:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,能持续站在梦想的舞台上
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.56,1:53:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来给你作保证哦
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.73,1:53:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,请原谅我
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.33,1:53:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,请快住手
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.90,1:53:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,安静点
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.50,1:53:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,会被学生听见哦
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.48,1:54:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,掀开
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.98,1:54:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,裙子掀开
Dialogue: 0,1:55:26.97,1:55:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我说你们啊
Dialogue: 0,1:55:29.21,1:55:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是在自习吧
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.48,1:55:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,安静点
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.48,1:55:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,继续动作
Dialogue: 0,1:55:39.99,1:55:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: 0,1:56:03.48,1:56:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,很好哦
Dialogue: 0,1:56:06.48,1:56:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,1:56:09.78,1:56:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,给我好好地继续
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.48,1:56:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,给我拼命做哦
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.91,1:56:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:58:03.10,1:58:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,给我继续
Dialogue: 0,1:58:05.80,1:58:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:58:30.36,1:58:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这些考题都会出现在入学考中哦
Dialogue: 0,1:58:32.53,1:58:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:58:34.49,1:58:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,会出来哦
Dialogue: 0,1:58:38.00,1:58:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对会出来哦
Dialogue: 0,1:58:39.80,1:58:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:59:55.98,1:59:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,1:59:58.98,1:59:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:59:59.95,2:00:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,古平
Dialogue: 0,2:00:01.05,2:00:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,想商量升学未来方向
Dialogue: 0,2:00:20.50,2:00:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:00:21.90,2:00:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你成绩很优秀 保持这样下去
Dialogue: 0,2:00:25.31,2:00:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一定能考进想进的学校的
Dialogue: 0,2:00:28.14,2:00:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那个啊
Dialogue: 0,2:00:30.48,2:00:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,已经厌烦念书了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:00:33.38,2:00:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:00:34.65,2:00:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,变得这样胆怯
Dialogue: 0,2:00:37.98,2:00:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,星宮老师
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.19,2:00:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是理事长的亲戚吧
Dialogue: 0,2:00:43.29,2:00:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是没错
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.49,2:00:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,指定校推荐能帮我弄点关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:00:50.23,2:00:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,2:00:52.40,2:00:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就算能这样做
Dialogue: 0,2:00:53.83,2:00:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝对不帮
Dialogue: 0,2:00:58.77,2:01:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,很强的正义感呢
Dialogue: 0,2:01:01.98,2:01:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,更不是只有性欲
Dialogue: 0,2:01:04.98,2:01:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,之前在上课时也插着按摩棒吧
Dialogue: 0,2:01:09.62,2:01:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,都看见了啊
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.88,2:01:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,还有之后让我们自习
Dialogue: 0,2:01:13.99,2:01:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,帮主任老师口交
Dialogue: 0,2:01:22.00,2:01:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,推荐是肯定要你做的
Dialogue: 0,2:01:25.20,2:01:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,还有 也不要让橄榄球社废社
Dialogue: 0,2:01:29.94,2:01:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,能跟理事长说吧
Dialogue: 0,2:01:33.87,2:01:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,连你也
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.97,2:01:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,做这种事
Dialogue: 0,2:01:39.48,2:01:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,退一旁
Dialogue: 0,2:01:46.79,2:01:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,星宮老师
Dialogue: 0,2:01:51.99,2:01:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这些家伙们每天不断学习
Dialogue: 0,2:01:54.89,2:01:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,积了很多性欲呢
Dialogue: 0,2:01:58.50,2:02:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,来跟我们做啊
Dialogue: 0,2:02:02.50,2:02:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,说好呢
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.97,2:02:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,2:02:07.97,2:02:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,才没不行吧 老师
Dialogue: 0,2:02:12.48,2:02:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都很迷恋老师的身体呢
Dialogue: 0,2:02:15.68,2:02:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊 老师
Dialogue: 0,2:02:22.19,2:02:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,星宮老师是怎样的
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.19,2:02:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,学生都知道的
Dialogue: 0,2:02:27.49,2:02:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:02:30.00,2:02:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,大家来抚摸吧
Dialogue: 0,2:02:33.30,2:02:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我们啊
Dialogue: 0,2:02:34.67,2:02:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,每天都在学习
Dialogue: 0,2:02:36.50,2:02:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 累积很多呢
Dialogue: 0,2:02:38.67,2:02:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不是很好吗？老师
Dialogue: 0,2:02:52.49,2:02:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,星宮老师是怎样的\N是知道的哦
Dialogue: 0,2:03:11.47,2:03:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,2:03:26.99,2:03:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,看着老师的舌头摆动哦
Dialogue: 0,2:03:43.00,2:03:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真下流
Dialogue: 0,2:03:45.47,2:03:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:03:48.17,2:03:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我也可以亲嘴吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:03:51.18,2:03:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:03:51.78,2:03:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,2:03:54.48,2:03:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,又没关系
Dialogue: 0,2:04:10.10,2:04:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙很热心学习
Dialogue: 0,2:04:13.13,2:04:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,至少能给他这样爽啊
Dialogue: 0,2:04:23.48,2:04:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,老师身材真的很好呢
Dialogue: 0,2:04:55.48,2:04:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好好地把性欲教导给学生啊
Dialogue: 0,2:05:01.98,2:05:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,老师请教我们啊
Dialogue: 0,2:05:06.29,2:05:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:05:07.19,2:05:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,老师请教我们啊
Dialogue: 0,2:05:09.49,2:05:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,2:05:11.02,2:05:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,最喜欢这种黑色的丝袜了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:05:15.19,2:05:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,能穿破丝袜闻内裤的味道吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:05:19.50,2:05:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,2:05:20.53,2:05:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,2:05:21.43,2:05:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,2:05:22.30,2:05:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,老师被大家这样弄 感觉到了吧
Dialogue: 0,2:05:47.99,2:05:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,老师被这样闻很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,2:05:50.76,2:05:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,很…
Dialogue: 0,2:05:52.53,2:05:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,很害羞
Dialogue: 0,2:05:54.10,2:05:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,说害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,2:05:58.27,2:06:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这样害羞却做这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,2:06:01.77,2:06:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 快住手
Dialogue: 0,2:06:03.48,2:06:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你们
Dialogue: 0,2:06:08.55,2:06:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 老师
Dialogue: 0,2:06:20.49,2:06:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,2:06:25.50,2:06:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,平常也会用这吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:06:28.00,2:06:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,才没用
Dialogue: 0,2:06:34.47,2:06:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,在学生面前说实话啊
Dialogue: 0,2:06:37.14,2:06:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没在用
Dialogue: 0,2:06:39.55,2:06:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不能说谎吧 老师
Dialogue: 0,2:06:43.78,2:06:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,全都碰触到了呢 老师
Dialogue: 0,2:06:56.50,2:06:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,2:06:57.73,2:06:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,2:06:58.73,2:07:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,学生们很在意哪里舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,2:07:03.20,2:07:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,说明一下啊 老师
Dialogue: 0,2:07:05.07,2:07:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,老师快告诉我们啊
Dialogue: 0,2:07:12.78,2:07:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,想听老师亲口说呢
Dialogue: 0,2:07:17.18,2:07:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能说那种事吧
Dialogue: 0,2:07:20.49,2:07:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,教导学生是老师的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,2:07:24.99,2:07:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,请用容易懂的方式告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,2:07:30.20,2:07:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不说
Dialogue: 0,2:07:36.00,2:07:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,能告诉我们吗？为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,2:07:38.74,2:07:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,2:07:39.47,2:07:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,2:07:46.98,2:07:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,2:07:51.48,2:07:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,2:07:55.49,2:07:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,老师跳舞啊
Dialogue: 0,2:07:59.99,2:08:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有听见吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:08:01.53,2:08:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:08:02.73,2:08:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里跳舞啊
Dialogue: 0,2:08:09.50,2:08:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,会打分数吧
Dialogue: 0,2:08:12.24,2:08:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,打我们可爱老师的分数
Dialogue: 0,2:08:15.54,2:08:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,2:08:16.84,2:08:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,快摆动啊 老师
Dialogue: 0,2:08:22.48,2:08:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,听不懂吗？老师
Dialogue: 0,2:08:25.85,2:08:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这样舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,2:08:53.48,2:08:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,扣一分
Dialogue: 0,2:08:59.99,2:09:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,快点告诉我们答案啊
Dialogue: 0,2:09:06.49,2:09:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,阴蒂
Dialogue: 0,2:09:08.29,2:09:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是最舒服的
Dialogue: 0,2:09:14.00,2:09:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,阴蒂是最舒服的
Dialogue: 0,2:09:16.14,2:09:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,阴蒂是什么？
Dialogue: 0,2:09:19.17,2:09:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这样马虎 当老师这样好吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:09:24.98,2:09:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴的
Dialogue: 0,2:09:28.48,2:09:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,里面的部分
Dialogue: 0,2:09:32.49,2:09:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,里面的什么？
Dialogue: 0,2:09:36.99,2:09:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,里面的
Dialogue: 0,2:09:41.69,2:09:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,里面的颗粒的地方
Dialogue: 0,2:09:46.43,2:09:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就是阴蒂的略称呢 如何？
Dialogue: 0,2:09:49.30,2:09:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真简单的略称呢 老师
Dialogue: 0,2:09:51.77,2:09:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 就只有阴蒂还是不知道
Dialogue: 0,2:09:54.24,2:09:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也
Dialogue: 0,2:09:55.84,2:09:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,全部
Dialogue: 0,2:09:59.98,2:10:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 剩下的若不说的话
Dialogue: 0,2:10:03.48,2:10:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,老师不及格哦
Dialogue: 0,2:10:04.75,2:10:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,其他都没猜中呢
Dialogue: 0,2:10:09.19,2:10:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是哪里呢？再弄强点啊
Dialogue: 0,2:10:12.32,2:10:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴的？
Dialogue: 0,2:10:13.79,2:10:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,2:10:15.53,2:10:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,阴蒂
Dialogue: 0,2:10:19.50,2:10:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,答案太慢了
Dialogue: 0,2:10:21.57,2:10:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,来处罚
Dialogue: 0,2:10:28.97,2:10:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,2:10:29.78,2:10:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不用弄这么强
Dialogue: 0,2:10:44.49,2:10:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,2:11:03.11,2:11:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,老师是不是变舒服了？
Dialogue: 0,2:11:06.18,2:11:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,老师这边有确实碰触到吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:11:16.49,2:11:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,老师很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,2:11:22.19,2:11:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,胸部也
Dialogue: 0,2:11:35.47,2:11:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,2:11:36.71,2:11:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,腰
Dialogue: 0,2:11:38.24,2:11:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,动得很激烈呢
Dialogue: 0,2:11:45.99,2:11:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,老师变舒服没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,2:11:54.49,2:11:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,老师啊
Dialogue: 0,2:11:55.96,2:11:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,快站不住了吧
Dialogue: 0,2:11:59.50,2:12:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系哦 站不住坐着也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,2:12:08.27,2:12:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:12:26.19,2:12:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:12:29.09,2:12:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,丝袜都湿黏在屁股上了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:12:34.20,2:12:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我想应该不会这样
Dialogue: 0,2:12:37.97,2:12:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好好地坐着吧
Dialogue: 0,2:12:44.48,2:12:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,让学生们能看得见
Dialogue: 0,2:13:06.00,2:13:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,腰正在动呢
Dialogue: 0,2:13:19.98,2:13:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好好地
Dialogue: 0,2:13:21.11,2:13:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真的流汗了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:13:26.79,2:13:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,电按棒要确实地碰触到啊 老师
Dialogue: 0,2:13:44.50,2:13:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 是让腰扭动\N还是腰自己动起来了呢？
Dialogue: 0,2:13:50.98,2:13:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,腰自己动起来了
Dialogue: 0,2:13:56.18,2:13:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:13:58.98,2:14:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这边变怎样了呢？
Dialogue: 0,2:14:01.99,2:14:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,2:14:03.39,2:14:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,湿成一片了吧？
Dialogue: 0,2:14:06.49,2:14:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微确认一下哦
Dialogue: 0,2:14:10.00,2:14:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这样优秀的老师啊
Dialogue: 0,2:14:19.47,2:14:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:14:22.47,2:14:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,2:14:24.98,2:14:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,2:14:29.25,2:14:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这黏答答的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,2:14:34.99,2:14:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,2:14:38.19,2:14:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服的证据嘛
Dialogue: 0,2:14:41.49,2:14:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:14:46.50,2:14:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,腰正动着呢
Dialogue: 0,2:14:50.50,2:14:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,再让我们多看些啊
Dialogue: 0,2:14:54.17,2:14:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好好地回答啊
Dialogue: 0,2:14:55.77,2:14:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,0分哦
Dialogue: 0,2:14:59.48,2:15:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有在打分数 好好地回答啊
Dialogue: 0,2:15:04.48,2:15:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 被打多少分了呢？
Dialogue: 0,2:15:09.49,2:15:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,2:15:10.76,2:15:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不过0分有点惨呢
Dialogue: 0,2:15:13.96,2:15:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,全裸就一百分了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:15:18.00,2:15:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,2:15:20.00,2:15:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你们
Dialogue: 0,2:15:24.97,2:15:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,下面也想要舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:15:27.97,2:15:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,2:15:30.48,2:15:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,能舔胸部吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:15:42.09,2:15:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,看着
Dialogue: 0,2:15:53.10,2:15:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,学生的舌头舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,2:16:02.98,2:16:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 和电动棒一起帮你用哦
Dialogue: 0,2:16:18.99,2:16:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也让我来啊
Dialogue: 0,2:16:24.20,2:16:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:16:25.86,2:16:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,请看这个啊
Dialogue: 0,2:16:28.47,2:16:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这个叫做什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,2:16:32.47,2:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,2:16:34.47,2:16:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴的液体
Dialogue: 0,2:16:38.98,2:16:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这叫做爱液啊
Dialogue: 0,2:16:43.18,2:16:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,都弄脏了 舔干净
Dialogue: 0,2:16:48.19,2:16:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 0,2:16:55.49,2:16:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 这边也
Dialogue: 0,2:16:57.36,2:17:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好好地舔干净哦
Dialogue: 0,2:17:05.27,2:17:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,爱液都流出来了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:17:09.47,2:17:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,流出来了
Dialogue: 0,2:17:11.98,2:17:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢看啊
Dialogue: 0,2:17:16.18,2:17:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,爱液
Dialogue: 0,2:17:21.19,2:17:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,2:17:25.49,2:17:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,很好吃
Dialogue: 0,2:17:30.00,2:17:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,听见了吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:17:32.00,2:17:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:17:33.40,2:17:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,2:17:35.33,2:17:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,居然说自己的爱液好吃
Dialogue: 0,2:17:41.07,2:17:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翘高
Dialogue: 0,2:17:56.99,2:18:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,老师…危险吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:18:00.99,2:18:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,能…吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:18:16.48,2:18:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,老师…也能摸这边吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:18:22.98,2:18:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊 自己帮我摸
Dialogue: 0,2:18:24.45,2:18:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好色
Dialogue: 0,2:18:24.98,2:18:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,星宮老师 光这还不够吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:18:29.19,2:18:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,脸抬起来
Dialogue: 0,2:18:38.30,2:18:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,再用心点抚摸啊
Dialogue: 0,2:18:43.00,2:18:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,腰不要停
Dialogue: 0,2:18:49.47,2:18:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,2:19:05.49,2:19:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,变非常棒呢
Dialogue: 0,2:19:11.50,2:19:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,星宮 再来做更多吧
Dialogue: 0,2:19:33.49,2:19:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,要被插进去了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:19:45.50,2:19:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,老师知道什么插进去了吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:19:48.50,2:19:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,2:19:50.50,2:19:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们好好看脸啊
Dialogue: 0,2:19:55.07,2:19:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,老师的小穴很顺利地插进去了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:20:03.98,2:20:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,自己确认什么插进去了
Dialogue: 0,2:20:06.99,2:20:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,什么插进去了呢？
Dialogue: 0,2:20:12.79,2:20:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翘高
Dialogue: 0,2:20:33.48,2:20:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,2:20:43.79,2:20:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜欢这样呢 大家
Dialogue: 0,2:21:00.77,2:21:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 舒服的话就说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,2:21:06.18,2:21:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:21:09.98,2:21:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,想要舔
Dialogue: 0,2:21:11.98,2:21:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,老师舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:21:15.99,2:21:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能这样嘛 老师
Dialogue: 0,2:21:22.99,2:21:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,自己扭动腰
Dialogue: 0,2:21:25.50,2:21:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,会很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,2:21:32.97,2:21:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 现在大家啊
Dialogue: 0,2:21:34.87,2:21:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,正看着老师小穴被插的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,2:21:39.98,2:21:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎样的心情呢？
Dialogue: 0,2:21:43.48,2:21:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,非常害羞
Dialogue: 0,2:21:48.19,2:21:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,2:21:50.12,2:21:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,就真的只是害羞而已吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:22:10.48,2:22:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,按摩棒…
Dialogue: 0,2:22:40.97,2:22:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 就只自己舒服是不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,2:22:44.21,2:22:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,也让大家舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,2:22:58.49,2:23:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 学生们正在排队哦
Dialogue: 0,2:23:42.00,2:23:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:23:43.57,2:23:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,也让这边舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,2:23:47.31,2:23:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,让学生舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,2:23:52.48,2:23:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:23:54.48,2:23:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,就只是这样不会舒服哦 老师
Dialogue: 0,2:24:05.99,2:24:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,现在也可以 更深
Dialogue: 0,2:24:21.47,2:24:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,自己用力含
Dialogue: 0,2:24:35.99,2:24:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,2:24:37.99,2:24:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:24:39.32,2:24:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这边也含
Dialogue: 0,2:24:46.00,2:24:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这边的手也用上
Dialogue: 0,2:24:52.00,2:24:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,2:24:55.47,2:24:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,老师的手超棒的呢
Dialogue: 0,2:25:01.48,2:25:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还有很多肉棒哦
Dialogue: 0,2:25:11.19,2:25:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,里面的肉棒也撸一下啊
Dialogue: 0,2:25:28.97,2:25:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吧 这个
Dialogue: 0,2:25:32.18,2:25:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,最喜欢了吧 老师
Dialogue: 0,2:26:03.98,2:26:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,快抚弄啊
Dialogue: 0,2:26:09.98,2:26:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,吃到最里面
Dialogue: 0,2:26:18.99,2:26:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,快帮我撸啊
Dialogue: 0,2:26:22.19,2:26:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这边也…啊
Dialogue: 0,2:26:36.47,2:26:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 这边也拜托了
Dialogue: 0,2:26:48.49,2:26:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 嘴巴也很色呢
Dialogue: 0,2:27:00.50,2:27:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样吃着
Dialogue: 0,2:27:13.48,2:27:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,只用玩具不够吧
Dialogue: 0,2:27:21.99,2:27:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这样湿答答了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:27:25.99,2:27:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:27:31.20,2:27:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:27:32.90,2:27:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看着吗？这个
Dialogue: 0,2:27:34.50,2:27:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,非常湿答答的哦
Dialogue: 0,2:27:40.47,2:27:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,2:27:50.18,2:27:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,手抓好啊
Dialogue: 0,2:28:06.50,2:28:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这么多肉棒 幸福吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:28:10.50,2:28:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,很幸福
Dialogue: 0,2:28:15.97,2:28:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:28:18.51,2:28:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,帮学生口交最棒了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:28:32.49,2:28:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,口交按顺序
Dialogue: 0,2:28:37.20,2:28:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,学生…哦
Dialogue: 0,2:28:44.80,2:28:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对大家都一视同仁爱着吧
Dialogue: 0,2:28:46.77,2:28:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:29:02.49,2:29:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 这个
Dialogue: 0,2:29:03.55,2:29:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉吧
Dialogue: 0,2:29:04.69,2:29:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们看啊
Dialogue: 0,2:29:15.50,2:29:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这也拿掉吧
Dialogue: 0,2:29:16.57,2:29:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们看
Dialogue: 0,2:29:31.98,2:29:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:29:33.08,2:29:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,下一位
Dialogue: 0,2:29:34.45,2:29:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:30:03.98,2:30:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,也看着插进去的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,2:30:14.49,2:30:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,2:30:18.20,2:30:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,还说快住手
Dialogue: 0,2:30:19.93,2:30:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你也很享受吧
Dialogue: 0,2:30:35.98,2:30:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 还有另一根哦
Dialogue: 0,2:30:42.99,2:30:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,脸好好地朝这边啊
Dialogue: 0,2:31:07.68,2:31:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:31:09.68,2:31:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这边有你最喜欢的肉棒哦
Dialogue: 0,2:31:13.65,2:31:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,自己动起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:31:17.12,2:31:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 腰再多扭动些
Dialogue: 0,2:31:20.99,2:31:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:31:32.00,2:31:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:31:33.14,2:31:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,还有很多肉棒哦
Dialogue: 0,2:32:19.98,2:32:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒先出来
Dialogue: 0,2:32:39.47,2:32:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,老师舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:32:42.47,2:32:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:32:45.58,2:32:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里舒服 告诉我们啊
Dialogue: 0,2:32:49.21,2:32:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都很舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:32:52.22,2:32:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴 胸部也…
Dialogue: 0,2:32:56.29,2:32:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,全都很舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:33:05.20,2:33:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,老师抓紧
Dialogue: 0,2:33:20.48,2:33:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好猛烈
Dialogue: 0,2:33:36.49,2:33:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,手伸长
Dialogue: 0,2:33:47.97,2:33:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,老师很色呢
Dialogue: 0,2:33:50.14,2:33:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,老师这边也
Dialogue: 0,2:34:01.99,2:34:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,抚弄肉棒 兴奋起来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:34:25.48,2:34:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 学生的…高潮了吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:34:31.98,2:34:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,正在看着哦 星宮老师
Dialogue: 0,2:34:34.49,2:34:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,2:34:38.49,2:34:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,2:34:53.97,2:34:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,搞得
Dialogue: 0,2:34:56.47,2:34:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,老师坐上来
Dialogue: 0,2:34:59.98,2:35:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒插进去
Dialogue: 0,2:35:01.85,2:35:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,自己插进去吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:35:14.49,2:35:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:35:19.50,2:35:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:35:33.48,2:35:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:35:46.99,2:35:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这边也弄
Dialogue: 0,2:35:50.19,2:35:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,尽情含 老师
Dialogue: 0,2:36:06.98,2:36:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,老师这边也
Dialogue: 0,2:36:19.49,2:36:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,再让我们多看些啊
Dialogue: 0,2:36:22.99,2:36:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒哦 老师
Dialogue: 0,2:36:32.00,2:36:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 喜欢肉棒吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:36:34.97,2:36:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,2:36:37.78,2:36:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,2:37:01.50,2:37:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,2:37:05.50,2:37:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,2:37:07.27,2:37:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢这个吧
Dialogue: 0,2:37:11.91,2:37:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒
Dialogue: 0,2:37:16.75,2:37:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,老师好好地说出来啊
Dialogue: 0,2:37:19.28,2:37:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢肉棒什么呢？老师
Dialogue: 0,2:37:24.99,2:37:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都好喜欢
Dialogue: 0,2:37:28.19,2:37:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是那样吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:37:29.33,2:37:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,能爽到自己所以才喜欢吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:37:50.58,2:37:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这么喜欢肉棒吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:37:53.55,2:37:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,退开
Dialogue: 0,2:38:27.69,2:38:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 这边也
Dialogue: 0,2:38:33.99,2:38:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,全都撸啊
Dialogue: 0,2:38:56.98,2:38:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这边也来
Dialogue: 0,2:39:28.18,2:39:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:39:29.31,2:39:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 朝向这边
Dialogue: 0,2:39:32.98,2:39:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,射在脸上也没关系
Dialogue: 0,2:39:39.49,2:39:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,要射在脸上哦
Dialogue: 0,2:40:01.98,2:40:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:40:12.49,2:40:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:40:37.78,2:40:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:41:07.48,2:41:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,学生的精液如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,2:41:10.98,2:41:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,非常地温暖
Dialogue: 0,2:41:15.99,2:41:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,被这样射高兴吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:41:19.99,2:41:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴
Dialogue: 0,2:41:22.79,2:41:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,还要更多吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:41:24.80,2:41:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,还有很多精液哦
Dialogue: 0,2:41:36.97,2:41:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,2:41:53.99,2:41:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,老师我也要射
Dialogue: 0,2:42:14.48,2:42:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,快看啊 老师
Dialogue: 0,2:42:21.49,2:42:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,要流下去了
Dialogue: 0,2:42:24.99,2:42:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,老师 能射在脸上吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:42:28.09,2:42:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,脸都弄脏了呢 老师
Dialogue: 0,2:42:32.50,2:42:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,要射脸上了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:42:53.78,2:42:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我也射脸上
Dialogue: 0,2:44:06.79,2:44:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,射了
Dialogue: 0,2:44:24.47,2:44:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:44:37.69,2:44:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,吸掉了吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:44:57.51,2:44:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,2:45:02.25,2:45:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,得拍个纪念照啊
Dialogue: 0,2:45:05.98,2:45:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,摆个手势
Dialogue: 0,2:45:07.95,2:45:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,得摆个手势
Dialogue: 0,2:45:09.79,2:45:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,2:45:13.49,2:45:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好好地看这边 老师
Dialogue: 0,2:45:16.99,2:45:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,2:45:18.53,2:45:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,2:45:22.50,2:45:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不要拍
Dialogue: 0,2:46:07.50,2:46:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,